d its federal funding for the region hinges on an approval process for the Metrorail Safety Commission, which must be federally certified by April 15. Metro’s potential decision to revert to its old hours could hobble that process, FTA said, because its staff would need to review its budget allotments to Metro to ensure they properly align with the transit agency’s safety needs under the new hours.”</p> <p><strong>VIDEOS OF THE DAY:</strong></p> <p>Stephen Colbert thinks it “would be insane” for Trump to declare a national emergency:&nbsp;</p> <div class="inline-content inline-photo inline-photo-center horizontal-photo"> <iframe width="480" height="270" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/TasnEtrFi78?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe> </div> <p>Conservative Bill Kristol posted a minute-long clip of Vice President Pence attacking Obama for using executive power in 2014:</p> <div class="inline-content inline-photo inline-photo-center horizontal-photo"> <blockquote class="twitter-tweet"> <p lang="en" dir="ltr">Mike Pence: The president usurping power and end-running Congress is "a profound mistake." <a href="https://t.co/GjDbHDvh0u">pic.twitter.com/GjDbHDvh0u</a></p>— Bill Kristol (@BillKristol) <a href="https://twitter.com/BillKristol/status/1096226782179557377?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 15, 2019</a> </blockquote> <script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script> </div> <p>Dorothy Butler Gilliam, the first black female&nbsp;reporter at The Post, spoke to Trevor Noah about her coverage of the civil rights movement:</p> <div class="inline-content inline-photo inline-photo-center horizontal-photo"> <iframe width="480" height="270" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/NlFVTtakQFA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe> </div> <p>Parkland s